{"tid":1438900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府想搶道德高地救民意，我地都要行動升級，輸出革命","createTime":"2019-08-10T02:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:24:23.000Z","uid":267881,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d53c84df726ab9181cee7cd33da1af905f6270","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"和理非冇效果？<br />\n勇武驚失民心？<br />\n<br />\n如果你執著尋找答案，就中左分化計<br />\n<br />\n政府加強文宣？<br />\n鄉黑群魔亂舞？<br />\n<br />\n如果你俾佢帶住走，又中多次計<br />\n<br />\n共 產 黨 嘅 行 動 方 向 其 實 已 經 好 明 顯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438170</a><br />\n<br />\n不斷中計中計，就會迷失，搵唔到出路<br />\n唔可以俾佢地消磨意志，但亦都唔好硬碰<br />\n唯一方法係<span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理、另覓出路</span><br />\n<br />\n你回想返，呢兩個月政府不斷犯錯<br />\n係因為我地破解晒佢地D狗招<br />\n佢地俾示威者lead住走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今次都唔會例外</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人只關心五大訴求<br />\n當上街權利都受到打壓，冷氣軍師三大方向：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1 行動升級，輸出革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[文宣組急入] 向中國大陸輸出革命文宣方向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437447</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【中港亦可團結】我們為甚麼麽挺身而出？香港抗爭者致大陸同胞書網絡熱傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436202[/size=1]\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436202[/size=1]</a><br />\n<br />\n短短幾日內，&rdquo;香港抗争者致内地同胞书&rdquo; 已極速在國內散播流傳，國內人民對真相的好奇心、對真相的反嚮、消息在地下渠道的傳播速度，成為我地嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n如果一個革命信息，一篇道破中共欺壓人民事例的真相，被廣泛流傳，會變成點？<br />\n<br />\n到時搞革命的唔係香港人，亂嘅唔係香港，引用華春瑩的一句話：「中國可是有十四億人民」，到時恐怕香港的外匯儲備都唔夠維穩費/軍費支出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2 文宣</span></span><br />\n揭破所有真相，官警鄉黑、支爆危機殺到<br />\n瘋狂forward<br />\n<br />\n有巴打起緊資料庫，去幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438380</a><br />\n<br />\n警隊濫權報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427712</a><br />\n<br />\n官鄉警黑，中共策劃元朗恐襲證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372823</a><br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨不想香港人知道的秘密<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437411</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3 諜戰</span></span><br />\n打著紅旗反紅旗，滲透內部分化親中陣營<br />\n<br />\n可參考小弟建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435000</a><br />\n<br />\n有文宣部，點可以無諜戰部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434887</a><br />\n<br />\n不停打擊TVB廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437184</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武手足請珍惜空檔時間練兵</span><br />\n<br />\n蟲系魔法師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434843</a><br />\n<br />\n水系魔法師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435022</a><br />\n<br />\n風系魔法師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435166</a>"},{"pid":"1aebfdd2c9cd1e23ab0ecb6847dda774fb6c1233","tid":1438900,"uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"寄信輸出革命，數目由警方決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438461/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5d677da06d8d085038d607728a819e89b140d7ae","tid":1438900,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b86c95050c63067c1976200bad01cce3ed8124ac","tid":1438900,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"民意要經濟支持<br />\n而家明顯支爆緊,外資流出香港<br />\n政府做緊就係推卸責任, 轉移施政失敗嘅視線<br />\n<br />\n岩岩中央統戰完，政府武力處於最顛峰狀態<br />\n不適宜硬碰硬, 靜待同默默製造下一個機會<br />\n例如罷買, 機場文宣, 睇外國知道香港赤化, 好醜惡唔好來香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n配合9月美國香港法修訂, 香港只會一直差下去<br />\n必須指出原因是靠近大陸=鐵達尼一齊沉船<br />\n到時香港政府根本挽救唔到經濟<br />\n<br />\n文宣上可以播下種子, 等大眾意識到大陸=鐵達尼<br />\n唔想沉就要自救<br />\n到時自然全香港都知要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1dd04581d18576a4b8d0bd5db608d0af2c9865","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:57:07.000Z","msg":"不要說「文宣部做野」<br />\n試著說「一齊做！日日做！」<br />\n<br />\n只要你有fb/Twitter/reddit acc<br />\n只要你肯去印文宣圖出黎<br />\n<br />\n你就係文宣部"},{"pid":"6505d427436acddf1fc1469c1ac0658c81e51c8a","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38d7dd61331d7f8b3a0c74cad861e19661a8f36","tid":1438900,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fc45856682907d26ca312a0e1a006e8ec4ffc12","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78335f369c239cc75ea7147f294b08c3d283c7cf","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"[黑警戰術] 新官上場, 黃大仙一役已明顯變陣, 各位手足留意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438314</a>"},{"pid":"b9a5ad39e63e60134f656f22316af6fe1acadc7a","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c9ffa3e8bc096871c57341e05d26d14baa720b","tid":1438900,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:20:12.000Z","msg":"贊成燒埋大陸"},{"pid":"b902812ea8f5cd59417159cbb41b8164ce4b6d3e","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef5f4bb338968be4c7881a4aeb26d133bbd4c37","tid":1438900,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3000d2d4d6b899701fe474be851ff860bf5f34a2","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:01:06.000Z","msg":"【香港終於有手信】派USB將文宣傳上大陸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438150</a>"},{"pid":"392fcb93c13d297ef190ad933e94331fd673bb59","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"內文記者傳﹕香港问题的来龙去脉都在这几句话里。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437579</a>"},{"pid":"a9f94704e4790c1899f1149751d20233159d4bf7","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe27b840721b0b86ddd25248da6ca74cd78ef95","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca42926a31b012dde566ed029d53a4c96128cf9","tid":1438900,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aebfdd2c9cd1e23ab0ecb6847dda774fb6c1233","tid":1438900,"uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"寄信輸出革命，數目由警方決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438461/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"【突發】一場金融抗戰 不信任港元<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1cfe70e76b1a23ca95b006c04424c8241f6ebfae","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:32:26.000Z","msg":"政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441970</a>"},{"pid":"0a889d627d6bdb72b4816247f6e0f54e27a60545","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"鏗鏘集好波 元朗黑夜超過330萬點擊 50點收視 仲整埋英文官方版！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1398116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1398116</a>"},{"pid":"ad93371866315609eb2a9c11c501216475b35d3a","tid":1438900,"uid":52748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲第22日<br />\n警黑合作 <br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問"},{"pid":"d741b9fa0952ebb5226cfac990bc8d750e2c4a09","tid":1438900,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"勇武派已經演化出五個屬性<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430432</a>"},{"pid":"b71d1bc05c8b88d8d90bc10fcee7c72267b4c090","tid":1438900,"uid":274022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a68fd3e395f61187fb206da0fca4333cebf5336","tid":1438900,"uid":274022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"大家唔好唔記得721嘅事<br />\n對白色恐佈說不<br />\n向反送中說不<br />\n不割蓆 兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n今日維園見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275559da71b6b6ba6559f62b1a7811de9b39108a","tid":1438900,"uid":274022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"大家唔好唔記得721嘅事<br />\n對白色恐佈說不<br />\n向反送中說不<br />\n不割蓆 兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n今日維園見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}